dct_title_s: Grundridsning af Öen Goree tilligemed dens Festrungs verker
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by bathymetric soundings.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
North oriented toward lower right of sheet.
Bar scale statement: Maalestav af 50 halve Favne.
Shows coastline, topography, shoals, anchoring points (indicated with anchor icons).
Town plan, featuring Fort St. Michael and Fort St. Franciscus.
Appears in Prévost's L'Histoire generale des voyages.
